#: ../../source/distributed_kv_cache.rst:2
msgid "Distributed KV Cache"
msgstr "分布式 KV Cache"

#: ../../source/distributed_kv_cache.rst:4
msgid ""
"Sharing and coordinating KV cache across multiple LMCache servers and "
"inference instances -- disaggregated prefill, peer-to-peer sharing, "
"multi-server coordination, and cache management."
msgstr "在多个 LMCache 服务器和推理实例之间共享和协调 KV Cache——分离式预填充、点对点共享、多服务器协调与缓存管理。"

